I am looking to sell the following lot of T206s. I have 42 cards which are all graded. They all range from PSA 2's - PSA 4.5 & SGC 30's - 50's.

((Please note on the PSA pics, it looks like there is a line going straight down the middle, starting from the top.....it's the pic / reflection and not the card))

Most of the backs are standard Piedmont and Sweet C. A few Old Mills, etc... are included as well. I can supply an .xls file with the names if requested. I have included the following links for the pics. Please paste the URL into your browser window to view. Please email me if interested. Thx. Pete
